{"tid":229991,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"提防暑期工陷阱","createTime":"2017-05-05T04:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T21:29:27.000Z","uid":70227,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4cbf6da91577a7bf1030b450ada90e8e797b1fc","tid":229991,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:31:36.000Z","msg":"又到左DSE仔考完試搵暑期工既時間<br />\n希望可以提醒下你地搵工有咩陷阱<br />\n<br />\n求職十大陷阱<br />\n(一) 上工前要讀課程或做無償實習 <br />\n(二) 層壓式推銷(傳銷)<br />\n(三) 賠錢及罰錢制度<br />\n(四) 無理解僱<br />\n(五) 騙取個人資料<br />\n(六) 欠薪<br />\n(七) 假自僱<br />\n(八) 利用青年來觸犯法例<br />\n(九) 違反僱傭合約<br />\n(十) 色情陷阱<br />\n<br />\n防範:<br />\n善用google查清公司背景,電郵地址係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費電郵如gmail,yahoo就唔好理</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公司話請你之後，小心檢查合約內容及附帶條件,切勿隨便簽署文件(適用係招聘前,後,入職至離職個日),簽署任何合約或文件前，要細閱所有條款，包括員工手冊。如有不清楚的地方，不要立即簽約，可要求帶走合約仔細研究，最多dse仔中伏就係俾公司拖糧/計少左糧但又無合約係手，勞工處想幫你都難，簽署時應該一式兩份，一份係俾你帶走既，如果無就應該堅持俾返份合約影印本你</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n保護私隱：身份證,銀行卡副本應在確認獲聘後（一般為簽署合約後）才需向公司提交，否則申請者只需在表格填上號碼即可（除非係大公司既要求)，<strong>寄cv唔需要有詳細地址,身份證</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係見大公司/公司地點偏僻記得同屋企人講聲<br />\n如果要你俾錢公司先就堅持身上得車錢同要求離開,建議你地銀包只放八達通同100~200蚊就算，<strong>千其唔好帶住信用卡／過量金錢去見工</strong><br />\n尋求協助：應上連登將內容加密發出求救，或諮詢家人或朋友的意見，有需要時可向警方及勞工處尋求意見或協助<br />\n面試地點:去非正式辦公室地址面試要提防,除非係自僱e.g幫人私補)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">用公司註冊處網上查冊中心查下你要見既公司係咪已註冊既公司，如果無就建議你唔好去見:</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.icris.cr.gov.hk/csci/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icris.cr.gov.hk%2Fcsci%2F&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=0258c6a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.icris.cr.gov.hk/csci/</a><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n1.<a href=\"http://yen.hkfyg.org.hk/page.aspx?corpname=yen&amp;i=5529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyen.hkfyg.org.hk%2Fpage.aspx%3Fcorpname%3Dyen%26i%3D5529&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=cb81ca70\" target=\"_blank\">http://yen.hkfyg.org.hk/page.aspx?corpname=yen&amp;i=5529</a><br />\n2.<a href=\"http://ezone2.ulifestyle.com.hk/channelnews.php?id=15485\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone2.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fchannelnews.php%3Fid%3D15485&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ec15e33f\" target=\"_blank\">http://ezone2.ulifestyle.com.hk/channelnews.php?id=15485</a><br />\n3.<a href=\"https://www.recruit.com.hk/Resources/ArticleDetail.aspx?articleId=29531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.recruit.com.hk%2FResources%2FArticleDetail.aspx%3FarticleId%3D29531&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=634d6716\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.recruit.com.hk/Resources/ArticleDetail.aspx?articleId=29531</a>"},{"pid":"d1247d85015d4f1b4fef66b7d1f36a277b95fb40","tid":229991,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"新法定最低工資水平2017年5月1日起生效<br />\n<br />\n　　由今日（五月一日）起，法定最低工資水平由每小時32.5元調升至每小時34.5元。<br />\n<br />\n　　根據《最低工資條例》，僱員不論是月薪、日薪、時薪、件薪、長工、臨時工、全職或兼職等，也不論是否按《僱傭條例》的連續性合約受僱，他們均受到法定最低工資的保障。惟法定最低工資不適用於留宿家庭傭工（不論傭工的性別、種族及國籍）及《最低工資條例》訂明的實習學員和工作經驗學員，以及《僱傭條例》所不適用的人士。<br />\n<br />\n　　殘疾僱員亦同樣受到法定最低工資的保障，《最低工資條例》為他們提供特別安排，讓他們有權選擇進行生產能力的評估，從而釐定他們應獲得不低於法定最低工資的薪酬，抑或收取按生產能力釐定的工資。選擇了特別安排的殘疾僱員，應獲得不少於按每小時34.5元的新法定最低工資水平來計算的工資。<br />\n　<br />\n　　此外，《僱傭條例》規定僱主記錄僱員總工作時數的每月金額上限，亦自今日起由13,300元提高至14,100元。當工資期須支付的工資少於每月14,100元時，僱主須備存僱員於該工資期的總工作時數紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n　　有關法定最低工資的查詢，可致電24小時電話查詢熱線2717 1771（由「1823」接聽），或於辦公時間內親臨勞工處勞資關係科各分區辦事處。勞工處網頁（<a href=\"http://www.labour.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=14b772ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.labour.gov.hk</a>）亦有提供法定最低工資的詳情。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2017年5月1日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間11時00分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201705/01/P2017042800776.htm?fontSize=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201705%2F01%2FP2017042800776.htm%3FfontSize%3D1&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=1ea2d51a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201705/01/P2017042800776.htm?fontSize=1</a>"},{"pid":"b2231d8931b4f1d62bcbddd067bbd162df0aa7e0","tid":229991,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:34:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個時考啲dse比班仆街呃左上去佢地公司話有暑假工 點知係到聽埋啲洗腦野係到分享on99 見到佢地啲認真樣扮撚曬幫你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後話有課程讀叫你報"},{"pid":"6acc6e52854973ed64dae279cfd8f560eac216ee","tid":229991,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:36:32.000Z","msg":"依家真係想搵返啲電話屌佢老母 放榜個日我啲成積唔好 係咁9打電話睇 講埋啲難聽野 屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06c8ea727aa9cb701de948b4496530b4b1040b1","tid":229991,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:36:56.000Z","msg":"觀塘某某公司好鍾意請暑期工 唔出contract 冇勞保 冇勞工假<br />\n人工壓到好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4ac3ac6a2c2a3000b24ed4ff41a989d136de86","tid":229991,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"dse仔考完試出校門<br />\n小心有班人叫你做問卷乜乜柒柒<br />\n千其唔好理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e1a40c8dff71384b28bc0ecff71519cf1eca10","tid":229991,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>觀塘某某公司好鍾意請暑期工 唔出contract 冇勞保 冇勞工假<br />\n人工壓到好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開名啦"},{"pid":"3e7c60ab40e129bef7d24c2a4ce49a2f289e0a20","tid":229991,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"54c8a925fd89ef3e4df105fa68f9c8e4791e981f","tid":229991,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:11:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab3b5d47e8a4a7148a5bb1e1a2ddc80f1e3c96ea","tid":229991,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8323a67f6ed77769a4cd78ab7e51b836e2d42eb","tid":229991,"uid":32635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c109028d396d87f04824055b7786b928f928da","tid":229991,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:39:07.000Z","msg":"做倉點睇"},{"pid":"13fc540f24e559b8e58698d02ad6451e82abb97f","tid":229991,"uid":29241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:09:29.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打話我知apXXo呢間野做得過？前幾日first in完等second<br />\n招聘post又話推廣下商舖，上到去又話幫慈善機構,上網睇又話好伏，Google 佢個電話又話求職陷阱，求巴打們講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def78aa7b6d470450bc50172d589520bcb7eb0e2","tid":229991,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打話我知apXXo呢間野做得過？前幾日first in完等second<br />\n招聘post又話推廣下商舖，上到去又話幫慈善機構,上網睇又話好伏，Google 佢個電話又話求職陷阱，求巴打們講下